Title: BalanceKing Application spec

Description of the problem:
  BalanceKing wants to add tooltips to their plots to make it easier for clients
  to understand. I will create a hardcoded example showing that I understand the
  libraries and how to add tooltips.

Description of files:
  libTest.py:
    Learning to use the Plotly library on some basic data. Eventually I want to 
    use this to make a demo for the client.

